<br>
Melee in genereal are broken when it comes to PoP, SoE made the most bassackwards way of making MoBs I ever heard of.  It seriously pisses me off to see a level 55 druid quad kiting @#%$ in PoV that when I ding 65 could not possibly dream of soloing ONE.  that my friends is broken.  The whole 60 to 65 @#%$...was just that bullshit.  We got no new disciplines, our skills showed diminsished returns, basically all we got was DMG bonus.  Where as casters got EXPONENTIAL growth through their spells.  I hate it when people say &quot;Well uhm, you guys got new armor and weapons in PoP&quot;.  Hrm..last time I checked SO does my twink shaman.<br>
<br>
SoE has declared melee to be inbalenced compared to casters and they are right.  But just like they declared the monk nerf was wrong 6 months before they &quot;fixed&quot; it...I feel that the balence between melee and casters will take much time and by this time we will all be playing EQ 2, not careing because we retired from this god-awful-yet-somehow-addictive game, or at the doorstep of Sony HQ with an AK and extra clips.  <br>
<br>
My point should you not feel the urge to read my paragraphs is.  &quot;Pure melee is broken&quot; NOT &quot;Nerf the casters but BOOST the melee in some non-game-breaking way.&quot; that and fix &quot;Taunt, I mean damn its been how many years? (3)&quot;<br>
<br>
my 2cp<br>
